}}'''Bahamas''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in December 2019. Its default cities are only the capital, Nassau.

In December 2019 on iOS; new countries were added. Along with the Bahamas; there was also [[Austria]], [[Costa Rica]], [[DR Congo]], [[Kazakhstan]], [[Kenya]], [[Kuwait]], [[Lebanon]], [[Mongolia]], [[Nepal]], [[Ukraine]], and [[Vietnam]]. This was added in the ''Friends'' Update.

